column16: What is your annual household income?
column17: What was your overall impression of this event (quality, lighting, sound, value)?
column18: Please share any other suggestions or ideas that would help us enhance your experience at Gesa Power House Theatre. If you would like someone to respond to your feedback, please include your contact information. Thank you!

column17: Had a great time. No complaints.
column18: Actual food, concessions instead of just small snacks would be great.

column17: Absolutely awesome evening! All the staff were incredible and my stomach hurts from laughing so much. My husband and I have really enjoyed our experiences at GPHT and look forward to future shows. All 4 comics were great - we would come see any of them again!
column18: All love and support to your staff that make these things happen! Thank you for a great time!!

column17: Besides the uninvited audience participation,  it was a great show. The sound was good, the comics did great,  and I wish we had more events like this to attend.
Great show. I hope we can get him back again in the future.

column18: With the VIP package we where never given the time for the meet and greet with Steve. I happened to come early enough to be told when and where at the venue.

column17: Well done. Sometimes the performer stepped back out of the spotlight, but I don’t know if you have hands-on spotters.

I loved the show!  The audio was very good.  I could hear and understand every word.  The lighting was perfect.  I loved the fact that WW has such a great venue at very affordable ticket prices.  The seating arrangement was laid out perfect.  The balcony looked like it had a great view of the stage.  The seating did seem to be a little tight.  I felt a little confined, but otherwise I had a great time.  Nice job Gesa Power House!
column18: I know this is a stretch but seating is a little cramped.  I know this would be very costly to change.  It was just a thought.  It won't deter me from coming to future events.

column17: I will not be attending this show again. To political me and my friend
Very entertaining. Production was done well, no issues.
column18: More headliner comedians and speakers please!

column17: Great event! We had a fun time. No issues with quality of lighting or sound.
